{
  "stem": "3380.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there from 1943 until-- we worked in the coal mines-- until January 1945, January 18.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they had orders that we should evacuate all the camps, and Jaworzno was part of that camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we start marching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with my brother, with my friend David Leder, and a lot-- what we were together from my town, some people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always used to stick together, you know, with certain people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were with a lot of nationalities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jaworzno was lots of nationalities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You got lots of Russian people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had some Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had Polish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From all over Europe, you find people-- French people, French Jews and non-Jews, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You got people from all over the world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We start marching in the evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the SS leader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said-- he came to us and he said that, we are planning a long and a heavy march.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever is not capable of walking or feels not to go with us should remain in here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were afraid to take chances to remain in here because we know that the sick people-- what they're doing to the-- the sick people, the people that aren't-- aren't capable to work.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we all start marching out, and we start marching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first day-- that-- well, if I'm not mistaken it was a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The first day, that wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By the second day, people start already-- they couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they start shooting left and right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You constantly could hear gunshots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People what couldn't walk were just pulled out from the line and shot to death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we marched [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] an entire week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We slept sometime by a farmer.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
